dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents common landmark areas within the United States including military territories, hospitals, educational institutions, shopping centers, industrial areas, amusement parks, stadiums, golf courses, and cemeteries. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.U.S. Large Area Landmarks provides thousands of common landmark areas within the United States. The areas can be used as a cultural layer at local and regional levels. Each landmark is named.
